1
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,260
By the mandate of Heaven, the Emperor decrees:

2
00:00:55,660 --> 00:00:58,790
The late Border General Xie Lin was loyal and brave.

3
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:00,250
Framed by treacherous officials,

4
00:01:00,250 --> 00:01:01,450
he died with a false charge.

5
00:01:01,450 --> 00:01:04,040
Now, his son Xie Jingchen has presented a blood letter as solid evidence,

6
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:05,160
bringing the truth to light.

7
00:01:05,160 --> 00:01:06,620
Xie Lin is hereby exonerated.

8
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:09,160
He is posthumously titled Grand General Defending the State and Zhongwu.

9
00:01:09,160 --> 00:01:12,160
Xie Jingchen inherits the hereditary title of Marquis Zhongyong.

10
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:15,200
The three main culprits, including the Left Vice Minister of War, are stripped of their posts and imprisoned.

11
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,200
Their homes will be confiscated and investigated.

12
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,950
The guilty will be executed in autumn.

13
00:01:17,950 --> 00:01:19,950
The 300 soldiers who died in battle with Xie Lin

14
00:01:19,950 --> 00:01:21,039
are cleared of their tarnished names

15
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:23,370
and posthumously honored. Respect this.

16
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:24,950
Old General Xie,

17
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:30,200
we have waited ten years for this day.

18
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,200
I, Xie Jingchen,

19
00:01:39,539 --> 00:01:40,789
thank Your Majesty on behalf of my father.

20
00:01:40,789 --> 00:01:42,370
I will not fail the imperial grace,

21
00:01:42,370 --> 00:01:43,500
nor the people.

22
00:01:44,250 --> 00:01:46,700
General Xie, you were able to exonerate the Old General this time

23
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:49,330
all thanks to Prime Minister Qin, who stood his ground in the court against all objections.

24
00:01:49,330 --> 00:01:51,250
He took the blood letter and secret evidence you sent back,

25
00:01:51,250 --> 00:01:52,950
and pleaded with His Majesty for three days.

26
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:55,330
Only then were all the treacherous officials involved arrested.

27
00:01:55,330 --> 00:01:57,160
Prime Minister Qin specially asked me to bring you a message.

28
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,700
He said you are a pillar of the state,

29
00:01:58,700 --> 00:01:59,950
and must take care of yourself.

30
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:00,830
In the court,

31
00:02:00,910 --> 00:02:02,410
he will always have your back.

32
00:02:02,410 --> 00:02:03,830
Thank you, Imperial Envoy.

33
00:02:03,830 --> 00:02:05,450
Please also thank Prime Minister Qin for me.

34
00:02:05,450 --> 00:02:08,410
Prime Minister Qin has taken great care of me and the Xie family over the years.

35
00:02:08,410 --> 00:02:10,539
I, Xie Jingchen, will never forget this kindness.

36
00:02:10,539 --> 00:02:12,580
I'm going to the wounded soldiers' camp to see how the brothers are recovering.

37
00:02:12,580 --> 00:02:13,910
Take your time talking.

38
00:02:14,370 --> 00:02:16,450
A'deng, it's been ten years.

39
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:19,620
The tarnished names of my father and the 300 brothers have finally been cleared.

40
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:20,620
The grievances have been redressed,

41
00:02:20,620 --> 00:02:21,450
and the loyal souls can rest in peace.

42
00:02:21,450 --> 00:02:22,829
This should be a good thing,

43
00:02:22,829 --> 00:02:25,040
but I always feel something is wrong.

44
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:25,910
What's wrong?

45
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:27,700
General Xie, as a general,

46
00:02:27,700 --> 00:02:29,700
you should know the court rules better than I do.

47
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:31,120
Just three officials from the Ministry of War,

48
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:31,750
one Vice Minister,

49
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:32,500
and two directors.

50
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:34,120
Do they really have the power to cover up the truth?

51
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,620
They could withhold the border's provisions,

52
00:02:35,620 --> 00:02:37,250
suppress the secret letter from the reinforcements,

53
00:02:37,250 --> 00:02:39,500
keep the whole court from finding out the truth for ten years,

54
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:41,329
and even charge the border-defending general in the Northern Frontier

55
00:02:41,329 --> 00:02:43,410
with the capital crime of treason.

56
00:02:43,410 --> 00:02:46,000
Yes, they absolutely don't have that much power.

57
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:48,000
Back then, my father held the military power in the Northern Frontier.

58
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,370
If there wasn't a highly powerful person in the court backing them,

59
00:02:50,370 --> 00:02:52,000
three Ministry of War officials alone

60
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,829
would never dare to frame a border-defending general,

61
00:02:53,829 --> 00:02:55,360
let alone do it flawlessly.

62
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:59,000
And before your father's soul dissipated,

63
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,410
he used his last bit of strength to tell you

64
00:03:01,410 --> 00:03:04,000
that demon forces have infiltrated the mortal realm.

65
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,160
In the court,

66
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:07,140
there are traps everywhere.

67
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:10,410
These three officials are just mortal bureaucrats.

68
00:03:10,410 --> 00:03:12,700
There must be someone else behind them.

69
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:14,620
The real mastermind who framed the loyal and

70
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:16,200
colluded with the demons

71
00:03:16,329 --> 00:03:18,040
hasn't been punished at all.

72
00:03:18,410 --> 00:03:20,579
They are even standing in the sunlight,

73
00:03:20,579 --> 00:03:23,180
becoming the hero who exonerated your father.

74
00:03:24,790 --> 00:03:25,829
You are right.

75
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:28,910
A ten-year case won't end this simply.

76
00:03:29,540 --> 00:03:31,200
The real enemy is still in the dark.

77
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,800
We cannot let our guard down.

78
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,750
Thoroughly investigate the old case.

79
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:39,210
No matter where they hide,

80
00:03:39,500 --> 00:03:40,910
we will find them.

81
00:03:41,450 --> 00:03:43,750
Blood debts must be paid in blood.

82
00:03:47,370 --> 00:03:48,700
When I was eight,

83
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:52,490
my father brought me up to this city tower for the first time.

84
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:54,570
It was snowing that day too,

85
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:55,829
much like today.

86
00:03:56,660 --> 00:03:59,540
A'Deng, no matter if you are the Dudeng Lady on the stone stele,

87
00:03:59,540 --> 00:04:02,000
or an anomaly in others' mouths who can summon and ferry souls,

88
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,000
I believe you.

89
00:04:03,450 --> 00:04:05,330
You ferry the wrongfully deceased souls in this world.

90
00:04:05,330 --> 00:04:07,000
What you protect is the same as me.

91
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,160
It is the peace of the mortal realm

92
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,330
and the unsettled grievances.

93
00:04:09,330 --> 00:04:10,830
In the past, you walked alone for too long,

94
00:04:10,830 --> 00:04:11,910
searched for too long,

95
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:13,450
and witnessed thousands of years of life and death.

96
00:04:13,450 --> 00:04:14,620
You must be very tired.

97
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:17,040
From now on, whether you want to find answers from your past lives,

98
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,829
or investigate the hidden conspiracies of the demons.

99
00:04:18,829 --> 00:04:20,040
Whether you go through fire and water,

100
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:20,910
or to the ends of the earth,

101
00:04:20,910 --> 00:04:22,110
I will accompany you.

102
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,450
You ferry the souls of this world,

103
00:04:23,450 --> 00:04:24,410
and I will guard you.

104
00:04:24,410 --> 00:04:26,790
Xie Jingchen, I used to feel

105
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:29,700
that I was just a passerby in this world, but now,

106
00:04:29,790 --> 00:04:30,700
I know.

107
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:32,500
My home is by your side.

108
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:34,370
Okay, I promise you.

109
00:04:34,620 --> 00:04:36,580
We will walk together from now on.

110
00:04:38,580 --> 00:04:39,370
Okay.

111
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,460
We will walk together,

112
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,450
together for a lifetime.

113
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:54,370
How touching, sister.

114
00:04:54,370 --> 00:04:55,409
Have you forgotten?

115
00:04:55,409 --> 00:04:56,330
For three hundred years,

116
00:04:56,330 --> 00:04:57,580
every time you fall in love,

117
00:04:57,580 --> 00:04:59,000
he dies for you.

118
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:01,130
Why do you never learn your lesson?

119
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,950
Little General, I trust you have been well since we last met.

120
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,000
Back then in Kunlong Valley,

121
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,660
I personally sent your father on his way.

122
00:05:10,660 --> 00:05:13,460
I didn't expect to send you off too after ten years.

123
00:05:13,790 --> 00:05:14,620
It's him.

124
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:18,950
Even now you still don't know who is

125
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:21,080
the real enemy who killed your father.

126
00:05:21,330 --> 00:05:24,330
The real enemy has been in the court all along.

127
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:25,330
Sister.

128
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:28,250
Make your choice. Either come with me,

129
00:05:28,250 --> 00:05:29,950
and let go of this mortal love,

130
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,659
or watch him and the entire city's

131
00:05:32,659 --> 00:05:35,330
people be buried along with these dead souls.
